snippet.title: BABIES having FUN with DOGS - Your CUTENESS and LAUGHING dose of the day!
snippet.description:
When these little creatures meet up they furry little friends, they create moments to be captured! Luckly, we've caught some of them and made a great compilation for you :) So ridiculous, funny and cute! What is your favorite clip? :) Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!
